steps.instruction:
1. Remove the husks and silk from the corn
2. Stand each cob on one end
3. Slice downwards to cut the tops off the kernels
4. Scrape cop with the back of the knife remove fine bits from the cob
5. Place the corn in a large microwave safe bowl with everything else but the cheese
6. Cover
7. Microwave for 10 minutes on high
8. Stir once
9. Microwave again for 10 to 15 minutes or until the veggies are tenger and the rice is softened
10. Stir in cheese; rice will thicken as it stands
11. Serve
